vocabulary.definition: very fashionable or up-to-date in style or influence
vocabulary.example: The cafe in Nakazakicho had a trendy interior design with modern furniture.
The streets of Osaka's city center were vibrant with colorful signs and bustling crowds.
The cafe in Tokyo had a chic atmosphere, decorated with minimalist furniture and art pieces.
The cafe's restroom was immaculate, shining with cleanliness and fresh fragrance.

vocabulary.definition: full of energetic and noisy activity
vocabulary.example: The cafe near the river was bustling with customers chatting and enjoying their coffee.
From the cafe's outdoor deck, we had a splendid view of the river and the city skyline.
